Installation steps 
java : sudo dnf install java-17-amazon-corretto -y
tomcat ; sudo wget https://archive.apache.org/dist/tomcat/tomcat-9/v9.0.82/bin/apache-tomcat-9.0.82.tar.gz

sudo tar -xvzf apache-tomcat-9.0.82.tar.gz
sudo mv apache-tomcat-9.0.82 tomcat

Step 1
cd /opt/tomcat/bin
Step 2: Check files
ls
Step 3: Give execute permission
chmod +x *.sh
Step 4: Start Tomcat
./startup.sh

🌐 Step 5: Open in browser
http://<your-ec2-ip>:8080



